                    After All - Acoustic (2007)

Wiredrawn is a rock band from Ocean City, Maryland. They have 
headlined many rock shows / events in Maryland and Arizona. The 
band has also played with a great number of national acts such 
as Saliva.

Lead Vocals:	Nick Mikula
Lead Guitar:	Mike Willett
Bass Guitar:	Kevin Willett
